messages.reasoning_content:
I found the relevant code! Lines 1565-1577 implement the optimization for `((X & 1) + (Y & 1)) >>u 1 --> (X & 1) & Y`. This is exactly what we need.

However, let me check why this optimization isn't triggering for our test case. The test case is:
```llvm
%rem = and i32 %a, 1
%rem1 = and i32 %b, 1
%add = add nuw nsw i32 %rem1, %rem
%div2 = lshr i32 %add, 1
ret i32 %div2
```

Looking at the code on line 1565-1577:
```cpp
// Reduce add-carry of bits to logic:
// ((X & 1) + (Y & 1)) >>u 1 --> (X & 1) & Y
if (ShAmtC == 1 && match(Op0, m_Add(m_Value(X), m_Value(Y)))) {
  const APInt *AndC1, *AndC2;
